headline: The Smartest High-Yield Stocks to Buy With $100 Right Now
summary: UPS is a turnaround with a 6.7% yield and a price that's just at the cusp of $100.  Brookfield Renewable Partners has a 6.5% yield and a long runway for growth.  Enterprise Products Partners offers a 6.8% yield and steady distribution growth.
